# Questions:

- For every additional element, why you are adding it

  ```
  - SSL certificate:
    this encrytpt the request from the user and server to ensure secure connection
      and prevent loss of infomation
  - Firewall:
    protects the firewall from malicious code and threats

  - monitoring service:
      used to check the performance of each server to know its health
  ```

- What are firewalls for?

```
  They serve as a defence system for the server, it protects the server against threats
```

- Why is the traffic served over HTTPS

```
For secured connection and prevent loss of data
```

- What monitoring is used for

```
Montitor is used to monitor the performances level of our server
```

- How the monitoring tool is collecting data
  ```
  Agent Based monitoring - they collect information from the server operating system,application and services locally and send it to the cloud
  ```
- Explain what to do if you want to monitor your web server QPS

## You must be able to explain what the issues are with this infrastructure:

- Why terminating SSL at the load balancer level is an issue
  ```
  - increased load on the load balancer
  - Security concern
  - addition configuration
  - loss of end to end encryption
  - loss of client ip address
  - certificate management
  ```
- Why having only one MySQL server capable of accepting writes is an issue
  ```
  - single point of failure
  - scalabilty limitation
  - concurency issue
  - Backup and restore complexity
  ```
- Why having servers with all the same components (database, web server and application server) might be a problem

```
- resource imbalance
- single point of failure
- lack of specialization
- complexity in maintainace
```
